{"tid":537914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣電總局︰電視節目不用紋身藝人和嘻哈文化","createTime":"2018-01-23T06:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T15:12:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":94,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"549661083b44378f895017196fae772830eb5f57","tid":537914,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:43:01.000Z","msg":"內地進一步加強廣播電視節目的管理，根據內地傳媒報道，國家新聞廣電總局宣傳司司長高長力日前在宣傳例會上提出，廣播電視邀請嘉賓應堅持「四個絕對不用」標準，明確要求節目不能邀請有紋身藝人、嘻哈（Hip Hop）文化等，引起輿論熱議。 <br />\n<br />\n報道引述高長力透露，電視邀請嘉賓應堅持「四個絕對不用」的標準，包括「對黨離心離德、品德不高尚」的演員堅決不用；低俗，惡俗、媚俗的演員堅決不用；思想境界、格調不高的演員堅決不用；有污點有緋聞、有道德問題的演員堅決不用。另總局亦明確要求節目不用有紋身藝人、Hip Hop文化、亞文化（非主流文化）、喪文化（頹廢文化）等。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180123/mobile/bkncn-20180123104257935-0123_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180123%2Fmobile%2Fbkncn-20180123104257935-0123_05011_001.html&d=KrGHmv7ib0IYaiM55%2Fu05%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=3563b90a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180123/mobile/bkncn-20180123104257935-0123_05011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6023e07d5e0763dc68e139c58c134192eeeabc02","tid":537914,"uid":42487,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:44:57.000Z","msg":"GAI 就係咁被踢出我是觀眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04053afba9089b4eec60c7d36e40cd2591ac7db3","tid":537914,"uid":73340,"like":35,"dislike":1,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:47:23.000Z","msg":"紋左身果班點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要油返肉色先得"},{"pid":"c3316f22f4b71455cbfccc9bc27fae14853ddd24","tid":537914,"uid":10652,"like":198,"dislike":1,"score":197,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T06:53:06.000Z","msg":"中国有撚嘻哈（笑"},{"pid":"e4191a744fceabc884345963bdf00f4d5256116b","tid":53791